Class CommonSystem

    • mdx.toptrumps.common.CommonSystem

  • public final class CommonSystem
extends java.lang.Object
    Version:
    version 1.0 28 Jan 2015
    Author:
    martinellimi Description: CommonSystem.java This class creates a common space to objects that will be used until the game is closed. These objects can be accessed from all other packages. This class implements the Singleton Design Pattern
